Define palette/color

city_properties <-
  c("CAPITAL FUND", "PROPERTY ENDOWMENT FUND", "Vancouver Public Housing Corp")
pal <- colorFactor(
  c("navy", "red", "green"),
  domain = city_properties)

Draw map

leaflet(longlat) %>%
  # setView(lng=lng, lat=lat, zoom=11) %>%
  addTiles() %>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$Stamen.TonerLite) %>%
  addCircles(lng = ~lon,
             lat = ~lat,
             # weight = wtcpue,
             # color = ~pal(TYPE),
             stroke = FALSE,
             fillOpacity = 0.5)
